'''甲胺氢碘酸盐'''是一种有机盐，化学式为CH<sub>3</sub>NH<sub>3</sub>I。它可由[[甲胺|甲胺]]和[[氢碘酸|氢碘酸]]在冰水溶液（或甲醇水溶液<ref name=Xia>{{cite journal|journal=Chem. Commun.|volume=50|issue=89|language=en|issn=1359-7345|date=2014|pages=13695–13697|doi=10.1039/C4CC05960C|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=C4CC05960C|title=Organohalide lead perovskite based photodetectors with much enhanced performance|accessdate=2021-03-13|author=Hua-Rong Xia, Jia Li, Wen-Tao Sun, Lian-Mao Peng}}</ref>）中反应得到，蒸去溶剂得到晶体。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=136|issue=2|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=2014-01-15|pages=758–764|doi=10.1021/ja411014k|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ja411014k|title=An Inorganic Hole Conductor for Organo-Lead Halide Perovskite Solar Cells. Improved Hole Conductivity with Copper Iodide|accessdate=2021-03-13|author=Jeffrey A. Christians, Raymond C. M. Fung, Prashant V. Kamat|archive-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130194645/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ja411014k|dead-url=no}}</ref>它和[[碘化铅|碘化铅]]在[[γ-丁内酯|γ-丁内酯]]中于60 °C反应，可以得到CH<sub>3</sub>NH<sub>3</sub>PbI<sub>3</sub>。<ref name=Xia />

